Sharp Says It's Assessing Damages Resulting From Earthquake in Japan

-- B y   M a r i k o   Y a s u
-- 
2011-03-11T08:06:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-11/sharp-says-it-s-assessing-damages-resulting-from-earthquake-in-japan.html
Sharp Corp., Japan’s largest maker
of liquid-crystal displays, is checking whether its factories
have been damaged by the earthquake today, Miyuki Nakayama, a
Tokyo-based spokeswoman, said by phone today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
